articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
Hello! My name is Varun Dommeti, a Sophomore at
Dublin Jerome High School. Some of my interests are programming and
music!
About the Project
My project Temporary Title, will relate to music, but I’m
not entirely sure exactly what yet!
Goals
Display and modify data related to music
Create a visually pleasing website for viewing musical data
Take into account bias by asking others for opinions on website
design

“This is data science”

Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School
Data Science Bootcamp
